metadata.name: The Gift
metadata.description:
The most beautiful art for a woman is pregnancy, where at that time the woman is at the peak of beauty.
so I want to share this beauty in NFT form.

I feel my appetite fluctuate and somehow more crankier than usual.
but i am enjoying the strong kicks, every little movement of my baby, her every little hiccups.

seeing my body stretched along with my femininity.
and since early days, i've been practicing saying all the good things to my baby.
What i pray for her to become and how loved she already is.

how beautiful this jurney has been,Not easy but still beautiful.
